    <description
        value="Maps marital status codes as found in the CBB MaritalStatus, based on the BeCivilstate  to &lt;http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/marital-status&gt; as found in `Patient.maritalStatus` in FHIR R4.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;"/>
